                        <br />

                        <h4>Scope:</h4>

                        <p>Due to the rapid advancement of technology and its integration into every aspect of our lives, industries and businesses increasingly rely on electronic and communication systems and hence the demand for skilled professionals in this field is on the rise. Graduates of the ECI program can explore a wide range of opportunities in various sectors, such as Telecommunications, Electronics and Semiconductor Industry, Information Technology, Internet of Things (IoT), Robotics and Automation, Research and Development.</p>
